    public class PbMessageValueErrorParameterOffsetBuilderIetf
extends Object
implements PbMessageValueErrorParameterOffsetBuilder
    Builder to build a TNCCS message error parameter value with an error offset compliant to RFC 5793. It can be used in a fluent way.
